title: Diamond 3 Main Support looking for an( Diamond 3+) ADC Main!

embed.description: Summoner Lookup with statistics, ratings, LoLSkillScore and more for HappyEmpire, a League of Legends summoner on the Europe West region.

body:
Hello everybody!

I am currently looking for an Adc main to play with!

About me :

I am currently Diamond 4 and i main support since season 3.
I am 16 years old.
1. My main Support is {{champion:412}} , but i also play champions such as{{champion:432}} {{champion:12}}  and some more.

I do have a teamspeak server,

What you have to bring with:

Be atlast 16 years old
Diamond 4 ( around 50 LP-ish)
Willing to improve and taking the game serious/having fun aswell
Being able to speak English in an understandable manner
Doing shotcalls( in lane aswell, but i'll do them too)
Maining ur Role.

IF you are interested feel free to add me ingame!


HappyEmpire
